
1) count the java file is a directory in a recursive way
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------     
     ls -a -R | grep .java | wc -l
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------     
2) batch download  
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
cat Desktop/sss.txt|awk '{print "wget http://www.cs.ucl.ac.uk/staff/A.Finkelstein/fose/"pw$2}'
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3) add double quote for each line: xxx -> "xxx";
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
awk ' { print "\""$0"\","}' ~/Desktop/temp.txt
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4) get all specific java packages from all java file in folder.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
find -f . *.java|grep '\.java'|xargs cat|grep import\ org.apache.pig|sort|uniq >>allalss_pig.txt
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5   VNCViewer with screen resolution
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#tsclient -x /home/zhaoyong/MyShell/Vnc2MyDesktop.rdp
vncviewer -geometry 1916x1148 9.123.147.114:1
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




